snippet.title: Ubi Caritas (SATB) | Ola Gjeilo
snippet.description:
Ubi Caritas by Ola Gjeilo for unaccompanied SATB voices.

This remarkable setting of the familiar Latin text starts in unison evoking plain chant, and gradually unfolds into wider harmonies and a more modern harmonic language. Not unduly challenging, Ubi Caritas is readily accessible to good high school mixed choirs for concerts or festivals of any nature. 

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/ubi-caritas-satb-print-ww1386
